0.title: Duration by Monitor
0.query:
timeseries avg(dt.synthetic.http.duration), by: { dt.entity.http_check }
| fieldsAdd synthetic.http.duration = ArrayAvg(`avg(dt.synthetic.http.duration)`)
| sort synthetic.http.duration desc
| limit 20

1.title: Service Response Time
1.query:

| fieldsAdd service.request.response_time = ArrayAvg(`avg(dt.service.request.response_time)`)
| sort service.request.response_time desc
| limit 10
